The proof of the if statement (if b then C1 else C2) simulation, i.e. (if b then C1 else C2, σp) ≼ (if b then C1 else C2, σp'), is parted into two cases:
  • The label of b, i.e. lb, is less than the state equivalence label L, i.e. lb ⊑ L.
    This case is proved by lemma WellType_imply_TSim_If_labelleq_lb_l
  • The label of b is not less than the state equivalence label L, i.e. lb ⋢ L.
    This case is proved by lemma WellType_imply_TSim_If_nlabelleq_lb_l

lb ⊑ L

Lemma PStateApprox_ifelse:
  ∀ tpc1 ps1 ts1 tpc2 ps2 ts2 l pc envp' pc'
         (Hts_eq: ts_eq ts1 ts2)
         (Hlabelleq: labelleq pc pc')
         (HPStateApprox: PStateApprox (tpc1, ps1) (tpc2, ps2) l pc envp'),
    PStateApprox (ts1::tpc1, ps1) (ts2::tpc2, ps2) l pc' envp'.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct HPStateApprox as [HPStateApprox1 HPStateApprox2].
  split.
  - intros.
    assert (tpc1 = tpc2)
      by (apply HPStateApprox1; eauto with baselabel).
    congruence.
  - auto.
Qed.

Lemma pstateII_ifelse:
  ∀ b ps ts n rho t tpc
         (Hbexpinterp : BexpInterp b ps = (ts,n))
         (HpstII: pstateII (tpc, ps) t rho),
    pstateII (ts :: tpc, ps) t rho.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct HpstII as [HtpcII HpsII].
  split; auto.
  unfold tpcII in ×.
  intros i curtpc Hneq Hintpc Hin.
  destruct Hintpc as [Hin1 | Hin2].
  - subst.
    eapply bexpInterp_in_var_in in Hin; eauto.
    destruct Hin as [x [ts' [n' [Hinx [Hpsx Hin]]]]].
    eapply HpsII; eauto.
  - eapply HtpcII; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma tail_tpcII:
  ∀ ts tpc t rho
         (HtpcII: tpcII (ts::tpc) t rho),
    tpcII tpc t rho.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold tpcII in ×.
  intros.
  eapply HtpcII; eauto.
  right.
  auto.
Qed.

Lemma TSim_End:
  ∀ t l pc envp rho envs i ts ts' tpc tpc' ps ps'
         (HPStoreApprox: PStoreApprox ps ps' l envp)
         (HPCApprox: labelleq pc l → tpc = tpc'),
    TSim AEnd AEnd (ts::tpc,ps) (ts'::tpc',ps') t l pc envp rho envs i.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply TSimProceed.
  split.
  - intros sst sst' ac1 pst1 sst1 HSStateApprox HSeqStep HseqstII1 HseqstII2.
    inversion HSeqStep.
    subst sst1; subst.
    ∃ ASkip, (tpc',ps'), sst'.
    split; auto.
    + ∃ (S O); simpl; auto.
      eapply ex_intro.
      split; eauto.
      eapply SSEnd; eauto.
    + split; auto.
      split.
      × match goal with [H: (_,_) = (_,_) |- _] ⇒ inversion H; clear H end.
        subst ts0 tpc0 ps0.
        eapply TSim_Skip; eauto; try(split; auto).
      × match goal with [H: (_,_) = (_,_) |- _] ⇒ inversion H; clear H end.
        subst.
        destruct HseqstII1 as [[HtpcII1 HpsII1] HsstII1].
        destruct HseqstII2 as [[HtpcII2 HpsII2] HsstII2].
        split.
        -- split; auto.
           split; auto.
           eapply tail_tpcII; eauto.
        -- split; auto.
           split; auto.
           eapply tail_tpcII; eauto.

  - intros sst sst' Hfalse.
    inversion Hfalse.
Qed.

Lemma TSim_Seq_End:
  ∀ c0 c0' ac0 ac0' pc0 ps0 ps0' ac ac' envp rho envs i pc l t pst pst' tpc tpc' envp' ts ts' envp1 envp2
         (HTrans : Trans (c0, pc0, rho t, envs, envp) (ac0, envp1))
         (HTrans : Trans (c0', pc0, rho t, envs, envp) (ac0', envp2))
         (HFrom1: starparaSeqStep t rho (ac0, (ts::tpc, ps0)) (ac, pst))
         (HFrom1: starparaSeqStep t rho (ac0', (ts'::tpc', ps0')) (ac', pst'))
         (Henvleq1: leq_env envp1 envp')
         (Henvleq2: leq_env envp2 envp')
         (HTPCApprox: labelleq pc l → tpc = tpc')
         (HTSim : TSim ac ac' pst pst' t l pc0 envp' rho envs i),
    TSim (ASeq ac AEnd) (ASeq ac' AEnd) pst pst' t l pc envp' rho envs i.
Proof.
  cofix Hc.

  intros.
  destruct HTSim as [HTSim].
  destruct HTSim as [HTSim1 HTSim2].
  apply TSimProceed.
  split.
  - intros sst0 sst'0 ac1 pst1 sst1 HSStateApprox HSeqStep HseqstII1 HseqstII2.
    inversion HSeqStep; rename HSeqStep into HSeqStep_init.
    + subst.
      match goal with [H: SeqStep _ _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into HSeqStep end.
      specialize (HTSim1 sst0 sst'0 ac1' pst1 sst1 HSStateApprox HSeqStep HseqstII1 HseqstII2).
      destruct HTSim1 as [ac1'0 [pst1' [sst1' [HstarSeqStep [HSStateApprox' [HTSim' [HseqstII1' HseqstII2']]]]]]].
      ∃ (ASeq ac1'0 AEnd), pst1', sst1'.
      split.
      × eapply starSeqStep_ASeq_starSeqStep; eauto.
      × split; auto.
        split.
        -- eapply Hc with (ac0:=ac0) (ac0':=ac0'); eauto.
           eapply SeqStep_starparaSeqStep; eauto.
           eapply starSeqStep_starparaSeqStep; eauto.
        -- split; auto.
    + subst.
      assert (ASkip = ASkip) as Hskip by auto.
      specialize (HTSim2 sst1 sst'0 Hskip HSStateApprox HseqstII2).
      clear Hskip.
      destruct HTSim2 as [pst1' [sst1' [HstarSeqStep [HSStateApprox' [HPStateApprox HseqstII'']]]]].
      ∃ AEnd, pst1', sst1'.
      split.
      × assert (starSeqStep t rho (ASeq ac' AEnd, (pst', sst'0)) (ASeq ASkip AEnd, (pst1', sst1'))).
        {
          eapply starSeqStep_ASeq_starSeqStep; eauto.
        }
        assert (starSeqStep t rho (ASeq ASkip AEnd, (pst1', sst1')) (AEnd, (pst1', sst1'))).
        {
          ∃ (S O).
          simpl.
          eapply ex_intro.
          split; eauto.
          constructor; auto.
        }
        eapply starSeqStep_trans; eauto.
      × split; auto.
        destruct pst1 as [tpc1 ps1].
        destruct pst1' as [tpc1' ps1'].
        assert (ts::tpc = tpc1).
        {
          eapply starparaSeqStep_Skip_tpc_eq with (ac:=ac0); eauto.
        }
        assert (starparaSeqStep t rho (ac0', (ts' :: tpc', ps0')) (ASkip, (tpc1', ps1'))). {
          eapply starSeqStep_starparaSeqStep; eauto.
        }
        assert (ts'::tpc' = tpc1').
        {
          eapply starparaSeqStep_Skip_tpc_eq with (ac:=ac0'); eauto.
        }
        subst.
        destruct HPStateApprox as [HPCApprox' HPStoreApprox].
        split.
        -- eapply TSim_End; eauto.
        -- split; auto.

  - intros.
    congruence.
Qed.

Lemma TSim_gt_envp:
  ∀ ac ac' pst pst' t l pc envp rho envs i envp'
         (Hleqenv: leq_env envp envp')
         (HTSim: TSim ac ac' pst pst' t l pc envp rho envs i),
    TSim ac ac' pst pst' t l pc envp' rho envs i.
Proof.
  cofix Hc.
  intros.
  destruct HTSim as [HTSim1 HTSim2].
  destruct HTSim1 as [HTSim1 HTSim2].
  apply TSimProceed.

  split.
  - intros sst sst' ac1 pst1 sst1 HSStateApprox HSeqStep HseqstII1 HseqstII2.
    specialize (HTSim1 sst sst' ac1 pst1 sst1 HSStateApprox HSeqStep HseqstII1 HseqstII2).
    destruct HTSim1 as [ac1' [pst1' [sst1' [HstarSeqStep [HSStateApprox' [HTSim1' [HseqstII1' HseqstII2']]]]]]].
    ∃ ac1', pst1', sst1'.
    split; auto.
    split; auto.
    split; auto.
    eapply Hc; eauto.


  - intros sst sst' HacSkip HSStateApprox HseqstII.
    specialize (HTSim2 sst sst' HacSkip HSStateApprox HseqstII).
    destruct HTSim2 as [pst1' [sst1' [HstarSeqStep [HSStateApprox' [HPStateApprox HseqstII']]]]].
    ∃ pst1', sst1'.
    split; auto.
    split; auto.
    split; auto.
    eapply PStateApprox_leq_env; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma seqstateII_ifelse:
  ∀ b ps ts n rho t tpc sst
         (Hbexpinterp : BexpInterp b ps = (ts,n))
         (HseqstII: seqstateII (tpc, ps, sst) t rho),
    seqstateII (ts :: tpc, ps, sst) t rho.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct HseqstII as [HpstII HsstII].
  destruct HpstII as [HtpcII HpsII].
  split; auto.
  split; auto.
  unfold tpcII in ×.
  intros i curtpc Hneq Hintpc Hin.
  destruct Hintpc as [Hin1 | Hin2].
  - subst.
    eapply bexpInterp_in_var_in in Hin; eauto.
    destruct Hin as [x [ts' [n' [Hinx [Hpsx Hin]]]]].
    eapply HpsII; eauto.
  - eapply HtpcII; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma WellType_imply_TSim_If_labelleq_lb_l:
  ∀ rho envs pc envp t l b c1 c2 ac1 ac2 lb envp1 envp2 i pst pst'
         (HTTerm1 : ∀ sst0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) pst sst0)
         (HTTerm2 : ∀ sst'0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) pst' sst'0)
         (Hlabelleq: labelleq lb l)
         (HTypeSafe: BexpTypeSafe envp b lb)
         (HTrans1 : Trans (c1, lunion pc lb, rho t, envs, envp) (ac1, envp1))
         (HTrans2 : Trans (c2, lunion pc lb, rho t, envs, envp) (ac2, envp2))
         (HTSim1 : ∀ pst pst' : PrivateState,
             PStateApprox pst pst' l (lunion pc lb) envp →
             (∀ sst0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac1 pst sst0) →
             (∀ sst'0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac1 pst' sst'0) →
             
             
             TSim ac1 ac1 pst pst' t l (lunion pc lb) envp1 rho envs i)
         (HTSim2 : ∀ pst pst' : PrivateState,
             PStateApprox pst pst' l (lunion pc lb) envp →
             (∀ sst0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac2 pst sst0) →
             (∀ sst'0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac2 pst' sst'0) →
             
             
             TSim ac2 ac2 pst pst' t l (lunion pc lb) envp2 rho envs i)
         (Hl: l = gsp (rho i))
         (HPStateApprox: PStateApprox pst pst' l pc envp),
         
         
    TSim (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) pst pst' t l pc
         (env_union envp1 envp2) rho envs i.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply TSimProceed.
  split.
  - intros sst sst' ac pst1 sst1 HSStateApprox HSeqStep.
    inversion HSeqStep; clear HSeqStep.
    subst.
    remember (gsp (rho i)) as l.
    match goal with [H: SeqStep _ _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into HSeqStep end.
    inversion HSeqStep.
    + subst sst1.
      subst.
      remember (gsp (rho i)) as l.
      match goal with [H: BexpInterp _ _ = _ |- _ ] ⇒ rename H into Hbexpinterp end.
      generalize HPStateApprox; intro HPStateApprox_aux.
      destruct pst' as [tpc' ps'].
      destruct HPStateApprox as [HPStateApprox1 HPStateApprox2].
      rename HPStateApprox_aux into HPStateApprox.
      remember (BexpInterp b ps') as v eqn:Hbexpinterp' .
      apply eq_sym in Hbexpinterp'.
      destruct v as [ts' n'].
      assert (true = n' ∧ ts_eq ts ts') as Hveq
          by (eapply bexpInterp_eq; eauto).
      destruct Hveq.
      subst n'.
      ∃ (ASeq ac1' AEnd), (ts'::tpc', ps'), sst'.
      assert (starSeqStep t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1' ac2) AEnd, (tpc', ps', sst'))
                          (ASeq ac1' AEnd, (ts' :: tpc', ps', sst'))). {
        ∃ (S O).
        simpl.
        eapply ex_intro.
        split; eauto.
        eapply SSSeq; eauto.
        eapply SSIfelsetrue; eauto.
      }
      split; auto.
      split; auto.
      {
        assert (leq_env envp1 (env_union envp1 envp2))
          by auto with baseenv.
        assert (TSim ac1' ac1' (ts :: tpc, ps) (ts' :: tpc', ps') t l (lunion pc lb) envp1 rho envs i).
        {
          eapply HTSim1; eauto.
          - eapply PStateApprox_ifelse; eauto.
            eauto with baselabel.
          - intros.
            eapply SeqStep_TTerm; eauto.
            intro.
            eapply Seq_TTerm_TTerm; eauto.
          - intros.
            eapply SeqStep_TTerm with (ac:=AIfelse b ac1' ac2); eauto.
            econstructor; eauto.
            intros.
            eapply Seq_TTerm_TTerm; eauto.
        }
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        assert (TSim (ASeq ac1' AEnd) (ASeq ac1' AEnd) (ts :: tpc, ps) (ts' :: tpc', ps') t l pc envp1 rho envs i).
        {
          eapply TSim_Seq_End with (ac0:=ac1') (ac0':=ac1');eauto with baseenv.
          - eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
          - eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
        }
        split.
        × eapply TSim_gt_envp; eauto with baseenv.
        × split; eapply seqstateII_ifelse; eauto.
      }

    
    + subst sst1.
      subst.
      remember (gsp (rho i)) as l.
      match goal with [H: BexpInterp _ _ = _ |- _ ] ⇒ rename H into Hbexpinterp end.
      generalize HPStateApprox; intro HPStateApprox_aux.
      destruct pst' as [tpc' ps'].
      destruct HPStateApprox as [HPStateApprox1 HPStateApprox2].
      rename HPStateApprox_aux into HPStateApprox.
      remember (BexpInterp b ps') as v eqn:Hbexpinterp' .
      apply eq_sym in Hbexpinterp'.
      destruct v as [ts' n'].
      assert (false = n' ∧ ts_eq ts ts') as Hveq
          by (eapply bexpInterp_eq; eauto).
      destruct Hveq.
      subst n'.
      ∃ (ASeq ac1' AEnd), (ts'::tpc', ps'), sst'.
      assert (starSeqStep t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac1') AEnd, (tpc', ps', sst'))
                          (ASeq ac1' AEnd, (ts' :: tpc', ps', sst'))). {
        ∃ (S O).
        simpl.
        eapply ex_intro.
        split; eauto.
        eapply SSSeq; eauto.
        eapply SSIfelsefalse; eauto.
      }
      split; auto.
      split; auto.
      {
        assert (leq_env envp2 (env_union envp1 envp2))
          by auto with baseenv.
        assert (TSim ac1' ac1' (ts :: tpc, ps) (ts' :: tpc', ps') t l (lunion pc lb) envp2 rho envs i).
        {
          eapply HTSim2; eauto.
          eapply PStateApprox_ifelse; eauto.
          eauto with baselabel.
          - intros.
            eapply SeqStep_TTerm; eauto.
            intro.
            eapply Seq_TTerm_TTerm; eauto.
          - intros.
            eapply SeqStep_TTerm with (ac:=AIfelse b ac1 ac1'); eauto.
            econstructor; eauto.
            intros.
            eapply Seq_TTerm_TTerm; eauto.
        }
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        assert (TSim (ASeq ac1' AEnd) (ASeq ac1' AEnd) (ts :: tpc, ps) (ts' :: tpc', ps') t l pc envp2 rho envs i).
        {
          eapply TSim_Seq_End; eauto with baseenv.
          eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
          eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
        }
        split.
        × eapply TSim_gt_envp; eauto with baseenv.
        × split; eapply seqstateII_ifelse; eauto.
      }
  
  - intros.
    congruence.

    Grab Existential Variables. eauto. eauto.
Qed.

lb ⋢ L


Lemma Trans_nlabelleq_pc_label_eq:
  ∀ c pc rho envp envs ac envp' x
         (HTrans: Trans (c, pc, rho, envs, envp) (ac, envp'))
         (Hnlabelleq: ¬ labelleq pc (envp' x)),
    envp' x = envp x.
Proof.
  intros.
  generalize dependent Hnlabelleq.
  remember (
      fun (p1: Cmd×Label×Policy×Env×Env) (p2: AnnoCmd×Env) ⇒
        match (p1, p2) with
        | ((c, pc, rho, envs, envp), (ac, envp')) ⇒
          ¬ labelleq pc (envp' x) → envp' x = envp x
        end
    )
    as P.
  assert (P (c,pc,rho,envs,envp) (ac,envp') = (¬ labelleq pc (envp' x) → envp' x = envp x)) as HP. {
    subst; auto.
  }
  rewrite <- HP; clear HP.
  induction HTrans; subst;
    try (match goal with [H: TypeSafe _ _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into HTypeSafe end);
    try (inversion HTypeSafe; subst);
    intros Hnlabelleq; auto.


  - unfold updateenv in ×.
    destruct (Nat.eq_dec x0 x).
    + subst.
      destruct Hnlabelleq.
      eauto with baselabel.

    + reflexivity.

  - unfold updateenv in ×.
    destruct (Nat.eq_dec x0 x).
    + subst.
      destruct Hnlabelleq.
      eauto with baselabel.

    + reflexivity.

  - assert (¬ labelleq pc0 (envp'0 x)) as Hnlabelleq'. {
      assert (envp'' x = envp'0 x) as Henvpxeq
          by eauto.
      rewrite <- Henvpxeq.
      auto.
    }
    apply IHHTrans1 in Hnlabelleq'.
    apply IHHTrans2 in Hnlabelleq.
    congruence.
  - assert (¬ labelleq pc0 (envp1 x))
      by eauto with baseenv.
    assert (¬ labelleq pc0 (envp2 x))
      by eauto with baseenv.
    assert (¬ labelleq (lunion pc0 l) (envp1 x))
      by eauto with baselabel.
    assert (¬ labelleq (lunion pc0 l) (envp2 x))
      by eauto with baselabel.
    assert (envp1 x = envp0 x) by auto.
    assert (envp2 x = envp0 x) by auto.
    eauto with baseenv.
  - assert (envp'0 x = (env_union envp0 envp'') x) as Henveq. {
      eauto.
    }
    rewrite Henveq in ×.
    assert (¬ labelleq pc0 (envp'' x)). {
      intro.
      destruct Hnlabelleq.
      eauto with baseenv baselabel.
    }
    assert (¬ labelleq (lunion pc0 l) (envp'' x)). {
      eauto with baselabel.
    }
    assert (envp'' x = envp0 x). {
      eauto.
    }
    unfold env_union.
    eauto with baselabel.
  - unfold updateenv in ×.
    destruct (Nat.eq_dec y x).
    + assert (¬ labelleq pc0 (lunion gap pc0)) as Hnlabelleq'. {
        eauto with baselabel.
      }
      exfalso.
      eauto with baselabel.
    + destruct (Nat.eq_dec x0 x).
      × assert (¬ labelleq pc0 (lunion gap pc0)) as Hnlabelleq'. {
          eauto with baselabel.
        }
        exfalso.
        eauto with baselabel.
      × auto.
  - unfold updateenv in ×.
    destruct (Nat.eq_dec y x).
    + exfalso.
      eauto with baselabel.
    + destruct (Nat.eq_dec x0 x).
      × exfalso.
        eauto with baselabel.
      × auto.
Qed.

Lemma kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Assign:
  ∀ pc rho t x e po envs envp envp' x0 k ps' tpc' ps tpc
         (HTypeSafe : TypeSafe (pc, po, envs) envp (Assign x e) envp')
         (HkparaSeqStep : kparaSeqStep k t rho (AAssign x e, (tpc, ps)) (ASkip, (tpc', ps')))
         (Hnlabelleq : ¬ labelleq pc (envp' x0)),
    ps' x0 = ps x0.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct k.
  - simpl in ×.
    congruence.
  - simpl in ×.
    destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep HkparaSeqStep]]]]].
    inversion HSeqStep; clear HSeqStep.
    subst ac''.
    assert (pst'' = (tpc',ps')) as Heqv. {
      eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_State_eq; eauto.
    }
    inversion Heqv.
    subst.
    inversion Heqv; clear Heqv.
    unfold updateps.
    inversion HTypeSafe.
    subst.
    unfold updateenv in ×.
    destruct (Nat.eq_dec x x0).
    + subst x0.

    + reflexivity.
Qed.

      eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_State_eq; eauto.

Lemma kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Seq:
  ∀ rho t c1 c2 po ac1 ac2 pc0 envs envp envp' envp'' k ps' tpc' ps tpc x
         (HTrans1 : Trans (c1, pc0, po, envs, envp) (ac1, envp'))
         (HTrans2 : Trans (c2, pc0, po, envs, envp') (ac2, envp''))
         (IHHTrans1 : ∀ (k : nat) (ps' : PrivateStore)
                             (tpc' : TPC) (ps : PrivateStore) (tpc : TPC),
             kparaSeqStep k t rho (ac1, (tpc, ps)) (ASkip, (tpc', ps')) →
             ∀ x : Vars, ¬ labelleq pc0 (envp' x) → ps' x = ps x)
         (IHHTrans2 : ∀ (k : nat) (ps' : PrivateStore)
                             (tpc' : TPC) (ps : PrivateStore) (tpc : TPC),
             kparaSeqStep k t rho (ac2, (tpc, ps)) (ASkip, (tpc', ps')) →
             ∀ x : Vars, ¬ labelleq pc0 (envp'' x) → ps' x = ps x)
         (HkparaSeqStep : kparaSeqStep k t rho (ASeq ac1 ac2, (tpc, ps)) (ASkip, (tpc', ps')))
         (Hnlabelleq : ¬ labelleq pc0 (envp'' x)),
    ps' x = ps x.
Proof.
  intros.
  assert (envp'' x = envp' x). {
    eapply Trans_nlabelleq_pc_label_eq; eauto.
  }
  assert (¬ labelleq pc0 (envp' x)). {
    congruence.
  }
  assert (envp' x = envp x). {
    eapply Trans_nlabelleq_pc_label_eq; eauto.
  }
  apply Seq_kparaSeqStep_Skip_k1_kparaSeqStep_k2_kparaSeqStep in HkparaSeqStep.
  destruct HkparaSeqStep as [seqstate'' [k1 [k2 [HkparaSeqStep1 [HkparaSeqStep2 Hkeq]]]]].
  destruct seqstate'' as [tpc'' ps''].
  assert (ps' x = ps'' x) by eauto.
  assert (ps'' x = ps x) by eauto.
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma kparaSeqStep_End_PState_eq:
  ∀ k tpc ps tpc' ps' t rho ac'
         (HkparaSeqStep: kparaSeqStep k t rho (AEnd,(tpc, ps)) (ac',(tpc', ps'))),
    ps = ps'.
Proof.
  induction k.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    congruence.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep HkparaSeqStep]]]]].
    inversion HSeqStep.
    subst.
    assert ((tpc0, ps0) = (tpc', ps')). {
      eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_State_eq; eauto.
    }
    congruence.
Qed.

Lemma kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_If:
  ∀ rho t b c1 c2 pc po envs envp ac1 ac2 l envp1 envp2 k ps' tpc' ps tpc x
         (HTrans1 : Trans (c1, lunion pc l, po, envs, envp) (ac1, envp1))
         (HTrans2 : Trans (c2, lunion pc l, po, envs, envp) (ac2, envp2))
         (IHHTrans1 : ∀ (k : nat) (ps' : PrivateStore)
                             (tpc' : TPC) (ps : PrivateStore)
                             (tpc : TPC),
             kparaSeqStep k t rho (ac1, (tpc, ps)) (ASkip, (tpc', ps')) →
             ∀ x : Vars, ¬ labelleq (lunion pc l) (envp1 x) → ps' x = ps x)
         (IHHTrans2 : ∀ (k : nat) (ps' : PrivateStore)
                             (tpc' : TPC) (ps : PrivateStore)
                             (tpc : TPC),
             kparaSeqStep k t rho (ac2, (tpc, ps)) (ASkip, (tpc', ps')) →
             ∀ x : Vars, ¬ labelleq (lunion pc l) (envp2 x) → ps' x = ps x)
         (HkparaSeqStep : kparaSeqStep k t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd, (tpc, ps))
                                       (ASkip, (tpc', ps')))
         (Hnlabelleq : ¬ labelleq pc (env_union envp1 envp2 x)),
    ps' x = ps x.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct k.
  - simpl in ×.
    congruence.
  - simpl in ×.
    destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep HkparaSeqStep]]]]].
    destruct pst'' as [tpc'' ps''].
    inversion HSeqStep; clear HSeqStep.
    subst.
    match goal with [H: SeqStep _ _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into HSeqStep end.
    inversion HSeqStep.
    + subst.
      assert (¬ labelleq pc (envp1 x)). {
        eauto with baseenv.
      }
      assert (¬ labelleq (lunion pc l) (envp1 x)). {
        eauto with baselabel.
      }
      apply Seq_kparaSeqStep_Skip_k1_kparaSeqStep_k2_kparaSeqStep in HkparaSeqStep.
      destruct HkparaSeqStep as [seqstate''' [k1 [k2 [HkparaSeqStep1 [HkparaSeqStep2 Hkeq]]]]].
      destruct seqstate''' as [tpc''' ps'''].
      assert (ps''' x = ps'' x)
        by eauto.
      assert (ps''' = ps'). {
        eapply kparaSeqStep_End_PState_eq; eauto.
      }
      congruence.
    + subst.
      assert (¬ labelleq pc (envp2 x)). {
        eauto with baseenv.
      }
      assert (¬ labelleq (lunion pc l) (envp2 x)). {
        eauto with baselabel.
      }
      apply Seq_kparaSeqStep_Skip_k1_kparaSeqStep_k2_kparaSeqStep in HkparaSeqStep.
      destruct HkparaSeqStep as [seqstate''' [k1 [k2 [HkparaSeqStep1 [HkparaSeqStep2 Hkeq]]]]].
      destruct seqstate''' as [tpc''' ps'''].
      assert (ps''' x = ps'' x)
        by eauto.
      assert (ps''' = ps'). {
        eapply kparaSeqStep_End_PState_eq; eauto.
      }
      congruence.
Qed.

Lemma kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_While:
  ∀ k rho t b c pc po envs ac l envp' ps' tpc' ps tpc x
         (IHHTrans : ∀ (k : nat) (ps' : PrivateStore)
                            (tpc' : TPC) (ps : PrivateStore)
                            (tpc : TPC),
             kparaSeqStep k t rho (ac, (tpc, ps)) (ASkip, (tpc', ps')) →
             ∀ x : Vars, ¬ labelleq (lunion pc l) (envp' x) → ps' x = ps x)
         (HTrans : Trans (c, lunion pc l, po, envs, envp') (ac, envp'))
         (HkparaSeqStep : kparaSeqStep k t rho (AWhiledo b (ASeq ac AEnd), (tpc, ps))
                                       (ASkip, (tpc', ps')))
         (Hnlabelleq : ¬ labelleq pc (envp' x)),
    ps' x = ps x.
Proof.
  induction k as [_ | k Hind] using nat_ind2.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    congruence.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep HkparaSeqStep]]]]].
    destruct pst'' as [tpc'' ps''].
    inversion HSeqStep; clear HSeqStep.
    + subst.
      eapply Seq_kparaSeqStep_Skip_k1_kparaSeqStep_k2_kparaSeqStep in HkparaSeqStep.
      destruct HkparaSeqStep as [seqstate''' [k1 [k2 [HkparaSeqStep1 [HkparaSeqStep2 Hkeqsum]]]]].
      destruct seqstate''' as [tpc''' ps'''].
      eapply Seq_kparaSeqStep_Skip_k1_kparaSeqStep_k2_kparaSeqStep in HkparaSeqStep1.
      destruct HkparaSeqStep1 as [seqstate'''' [k1' [k2' [HkparaSeqStep11 [HkparaSeqStep12 Hkeqsum']]]]].
      destruct seqstate'''' as [tpc'''' ps''''].
      assert (¬ labelleq (lunion pc l) (envp' x))
        by eauto with baselabel.
      assert (ps'''' x = ps'' x)
        by eauto.
      assert (ps'''' = ps''')
        by (eapply kparaSeqStep_End_PState_eq; eauto).
      assert (ps' x = ps''' x). {
        eapply Hind with (m:=k2); eauto.
        omega.
      }
      congruence.
    + subst.
      assert ((tpc'',ps'') = (tpc', ps')). {
        eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_State_eq; eauto.
      }
      congruence.
Qed.

Lemma kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq:
  ∀ c k pc rho envs envp envp' t ac tpc ps tpc' ps' x
         (Hnlabelleq: ¬ labelleq pc (envp' x))
         (HTrans: Trans (c, pc, rho t, envs, envp) (ac, envp'))
         (HkparaSeqStep: kparaSeqStep k t rho (ac, ((tpc, ps))) (ASkip, ((tpc',ps')))),
    ps'(x) = ps(x).
Proof.
  intros.
  generalize dependent x.
  generalize dependent tpc.
  generalize dependent ps.
  generalize dependent tpc'.
  generalize dependent ps'.
  generalize dependent k.
  remember (
      fun (p: Cmd ×Label ×Policy×Env×Env) (p0: AnnoCmd × Env)
      ⇒ match (p, p0) with
         | ((c,pc,po,envs, envp), (ac, envp'))
           ⇒
           ∀ (k : nat) (ps' : PrivateStore) (tpc' : TPC)
                  (ps : PrivateStore) (tpc : TPC),
             kparaSeqStep k t rho (ac, (tpc, ps)) (ASkip, (tpc', ps')) →
             ∀ x : Vars, ¬ labelleq pc (envp' x) → ps' x = ps x
         end
    ) as P.
  assert (P (c,pc,rho t,envs, envp) (ac, envp') =
          ∀ (k : nat) (ps' : PrivateStore) (tpc' : TPC)
                 (ps : PrivateStore) (tpc : TPC),
            kparaSeqStep k t rho (ac, (tpc, ps)) (ASkip, (tpc', ps')) →
            ∀ x : Vars, ¬ labelleq pc (envp' x) → ps' x = ps x
         ) as HPx
      by (subst; auto).
  rewrite <- HPx.
  clear HPx.
  induction HTrans; subst; auto; intros;
    try match goal with [H: kparaSeqStep _ _ _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into HkparaSeqStep end;
    try match goal with [H: ¬ labelleq _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into Hnlabelleq end;
    try match goal with [H: TypeSafe _ _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into HTypeSafe end.

  - assert ((tpc,ps) = (tpc',ps')). {
      eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_State_eq; eauto.
    }
    congruence.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Assign; eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Get; eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Put; eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Out; eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Seq with (envp':=envp'0); eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_If with (envp1:=envp1); eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_While; eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Hsend with (e1:=e1); eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Lsend with (e1:=e1); eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Hrecv; eauto.

  - eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq_Lrecv; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma starparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq:
  ∀ c pc rho envs envp envp' t ac tpc ps tpc' ps' x
         (Hnlabelleq: ¬ labelleq pc (envp' x))
         (HTrans: Trans (c, pc, rho t, envs, envp) (ac, envp'))
         (HstarSeqStep: starparaSeqStep t rho (ac, ((tpc, ps))) (ASkip, ((tpc',ps')))),
    ps'(x) = ps(x).
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct HstarSeqStep as [k HkparaSeqStep].
  eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma starSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq:
  ∀ c pc rho envs envp envp' t ac tpc ps sst tpc' ps' sst' x
         (Hnlabelleq: ¬ labelleq pc (envp' x))
         (HTrans: Trans (c, pc, rho t, envs, envp) (ac, envp'))
         (HstarSeqStep: starSeqStep t rho (ac, ((tpc, ps), sst)) (ASkip, ((tpc',ps'), sst'))),
    ps'(x) = ps(x).
Proof.
  intros.
  eapply starparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq; eauto.
  eapply starSeqStep_imply_starparaSeqStep; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma kparaSeqStep_Seq:
  ∀ k t rho ac1 ac2 pst ac' pst'
         (HkparaSeqStep: kparaSeqStep k t rho (ASeq ac1 ac2, pst) (ac', pst')),
    (∃ ac1', ac' = ASeq ac1' ac2 ∧ starparaSeqStep t rho (ac1, pst) (ac1', pst'))
    ∨
    (∃ ac2' pst'',
        starparaSeqStep t rho (ac1, pst) (ASkip, pst'') ∧
        ac' = ac2' ∧ starparaSeqStep t rho (ac2, pst'') (ac2', pst')).
Proof.
  induction k.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    inversion HkparaSeqStep.
    subst.
    left.
    ∃ ac1.
    split; auto.
    eapply starparaSeqStep_refl.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep HkparaSeqStep]]]]].
    inversion HSeqStep.
    + subst.
      eapply IHk in HkparaSeqStep; eauto.
      destruct HkparaSeqStep as [Hind1 | Hind2].
      × destruct Hind1 as [ac1'0 [Hac' HstarparaSeqStep]].
        subst ac'.
        left.
        ∃ ac1'0.
        split; auto.
        eapply SeqStep_starparaSeqStep'; eauto.
      × destruct Hind2 as [ac2' [pst''' [HstarparaSeqStep [Hac' HstarparaSeqStep']]]].
        subst ac'.
        right.
        ∃ ac2', pst'''.
        split; auto.
        eapply SeqStep_starparaSeqStep'; eauto.
    + subst.
      right.
      ∃ ac', pst''.
      split.
      × eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
      × split; auto.
        ∃ k; auto.
Qed.

Lemma kparaSeqStep_Seq_k1k2:
  ∀ k t rho ac1 ac2 pst ac' pst'
         (HkparaSeqStep: kparaSeqStep k t rho (ASeq ac1 ac2, pst) (ac', pst')),
    (∃ ac1', ac' = ASeq ac1' ac2 ∧ kparaSeqStep k t rho (ac1, pst) (ac1', pst'))
    ∨
    (∃ ac2' pst'' k1 k2,
        kparaSeqStep k1 t rho (ac1, pst) (ASkip, pst'') ∧
        ac' = ac2' ∧ kparaSeqStep k2 t rho (ac2, pst'') (ac2', pst') ∧
        k = k1+k2+1
    ).
Proof.
  induction k.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    inversion HkparaSeqStep.
    subst.
    left.
    ∃ ac1.
    split; auto.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep HkparaSeqStep]]]]].
    inversion HSeqStep.
    + subst.
      eapply IHk in HkparaSeqStep; eauto.
      destruct HkparaSeqStep as [Hind1 | Hind2].
      × destruct Hind1 as [ac1'0 [Hac' HstarparaSeqStep]].
        subst ac'.
        left.
        ∃ ac1'0.
        split; auto.
        repeat eapply ex_intro.
        split; eauto.
      × destruct Hind2 as [ac2' [pst''' [k1 [k2 [HkparaSeqStep1 [Hac' [HkparaSeqStep2 Hkeq]]]]]]].
        subst ac'.
        right.
        ∃ ac2', pst''', (S k1), k2.
        split.
        -- simpl.
           repeat eapply ex_intro; eauto.
        -- split; auto.
           split; auto.
           omega.
    + subst.
      right.
      ∃ ac', pst'', O, k.
      split; simpl; auto.
      split; auto.
      split; auto.
      omega.
Qed.

    + subst.

    + subst.

      × eapply SeqStep_imply_starparaSeqStep; eauto.

Qed.

Lemma kparaSeqStep_While:
  ∀ k t rho b ac pst ac' pst'
         (HkparaSeqStep: kparaSeqStep k t rho (AWhiledo b ac, pst) (ac', pst')),
    (∃ ac'0 pst'' pst''',
        starparaSeqStep t rho (AWhiledo b ac, pst) (AWhiledo b ac, pst'') ∧
        starparaSeqStep t rho (AWhiledo b ac, pst'') (ASeq ac (AWhiledo b ac), pst''') ∧
        starparaSeqStep t rho (AWhiledo b ac, pst'') (ASeq ac'0 (AWhiledo b ac), pst') ∧
        ac' = (ASeq ac'0 (AWhiledo b ac)) ∧ starparaSeqStep t rho (ac, pst''') (ac'0, pst'))
    ∨
    (∃ pst'',
        starparaSeqStep t rho (AWhiledo b ac, pst) (AWhiledo b ac, pst'') ∧
        ac' = AWhiledo b ac)
    ∨
    (∃ pst'',
        starparaSeqStep t rho (AWhiledo b ac, pst) (AWhiledo b ac, pst'') ∧
        ac' = ASkip ∧ pst' = pst'').

Proof.
  induction k as [_ | k IHk] using nat_ind2.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    right; left.
    ∃ pst.
    split; try congruence.
    ∃ O; simpl; auto.
  - intros.
    simpl in ×.
    destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep HkparaSeqStep]]]]].
    inversion HSeqStep.
    + subst.
      generalize HkparaSeqStep; intro HkparaSeqStep_aux.
      eapply kparaSeqStep_Seq_k1k2 in HkparaSeqStep.
      destruct HkparaSeqStep as [HkparaSeqStep1 | HkparaSeqStep2].
      × destruct HkparaSeqStep1 as [ac1' [Hac' HkparaSeqStep']].
        left.
        subst.
        ∃ ac1', (tpc, ps), (ts::tpc, ps).
        split.
        {
          eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
        }
        split.
        {
          ∃ (S O); simpl.
          repeat eapply ex_intro; eauto.
        }
        split.
        {
          eapply SeqStep_starparaSeqStep'; eauto.
          ∃ k; auto.
        }
        split; auto.
        {
          ∃ k; auto.
        }
      × destruct HkparaSeqStep2 as [ac1' [pst'' [k1 [k2 [HkparaSeqStep' [Hac' [HkparaSeqStep'' Hkeq]]]]]]].
        subst ac1'.
        generalize HkparaSeqStep''; intro HkparaSeqStep''_aux.
        eapply IHk in HkparaSeqStep''_aux; try omega; auto.
        assert (starparaSeqStep t rho (AWhiledo b ac, (tpc, ps)) (AWhiledo b ac, pst'')).
        {
          assert (starparaSeqStep t rho (ASeq ac (AWhiledo b ac), (ts::tpc, ps)) (ASeq ASkip (AWhiledo b ac), pst'')). {
            ∃ k1.
            eapply kparaSeqStep_Seq1; eauto.
          }
          assert (starparaSeqStep t rho (ASeq ASkip (AWhiledo b ac), pst'') (AWhiledo b ac, pst'')). {
            ∃ (S O).
            simpl.
            repeat eapply ex_intro.
            split; eauto.
            econstructor; eauto.
          }
          assert (starparaSeqStep t rho (ASeq ac (AWhiledo b ac), (ts::tpc, ps)) (AWhiledo b ac, pst'')). {
            eapply starparaSeqStep_trans; eauto.
          }
          eapply SeqStep_starparaSeqStep'; eauto.
        }
        destruct HkparaSeqStep''_aux as [Hind1 | [Hind2 | Hind3]].
        -- left.
           destruct Hind1 as [ac'0 [pst''0 [pst''' [HstarparaSeqStep1 [HstarparaSeqStep2 [HstarparaSeqStep3 [Hac' HstarparaSeqStep]]]]]]].
           ∃ ac'0, pst''0, pst'''.
           split.
           {
             eapply starparaSeqStep_trans; eauto.
           }
           split; auto.
        -- right; left.
           destruct Hind2 as [pst''0 [HstarparaSeqStep Hac']].
           subst ac'.
           ∃ pst''0.
           split; auto.
           eapply starparaSeqStep_trans; eauto.
        -- right; right.
           destruct Hind3 as [pst''0 [HstarparaSeqStep [Hac' Hpst']]].
           ∃ pst''0.
           split.
           {
             eapply starparaSeqStep_trans; eauto.
           }
           {
             split; congruence.
           }
    + subst.
      right; right.
      ∃ (tpc,ps).
      split.
      × eapply starparaSeqStep_refl.
      × assert ((tpc, ps) = pst'). {
          eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_State_eq; eauto.
        }
        assert (ac' = ASkip). {
          eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_is_Skip; eauto.
        }
        split; congruence.

        Grab Existential Variables.
        eauto.
Qed.

Lemma starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_Put:
  ∀ t rho x e pc po envs envp envp' l i pst1 sst pst ac sst1 ac1 pst0
          (HTypeSafe : TypeSafe (pc, po, envs) envp (Put x e) envp')
          (Hnlabelleq : ¬ labelleq pc l)
          (HSeqStep : SeqStep t rho (ac, (pst, sst)) (ac1, (pst1, sst1)))
          (HstarparaSeqStep : starparaSeqStep t rho (APut x e, pst0) (ac, pst)),
    SharedStateApprox sst sst1 i l rho envs.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct HstarparaSeqStep as [k HkparaSeqStep];
    destruct k.
  - simpl in ×.
    inversion HkparaSeqStep.
    subst.
    inversion HSeqStep.
    subst.
    split; auto with basestate.
    unfold SStoreApprox.
    unfold updatess.
    intros.
    destruct (Nat.eq_dec x x0).
    + subst x0.
      inversion HTypeSafe.
      subst.
      inversion H7.
      match goal with [H: ExprTypeSafe envs _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into HExprTypeSafe end.
      inversion HExprTypeSafe.
      subst.
      assert (labelleq pc (envs x))
        by eauto with baselabel.
      assert (labelleq pc l)
        by eauto with baselabel.
      congruence.
    + split; congruence.
  - simpl in ×.
    destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst0 [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep' HkparaSeqStep]]]]].
    inversion HSeqStep'.
    subst.
    assert (ac = ASkip). {
      eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_is_Skip; eauto.
    }
    subst ac.
    inversion HSeqStep.
    eauto with basestate.
Qed.

Lemma starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_Seq:
  ∀ t rho c1 c2 pc po envs envp ac1 ac2 envp' envp'' l i pst1 sst pst ac sst1 ac3 pst0
         (HTrans1 : Trans (c1, pc, po, envs, envp) (ac1, envp'))
         (HTrans2 : Trans (c2, pc, po, envs, envp') (ac2, envp''))
         (IHHTrans1 : ∀ l : Label,
             ¬ labelleq pc l →
             ∀ (i : Tid) (pst1 : PrivateState) (sst : SharedState)
                    (pst : PrivateState) (ac : AnnoCmd) (sst1 : SharedState)
                    (ac2 : AnnoCmd),
               l = gsp (rho i) →
               pstateII pst t rho →
               SeqStep t rho (ac, (pst, sst)) (ac2, (pst1, sst1)) →
               ∀ pst0 : PrivateState,
                 starparaSeqStep t rho (ac1, pst0) (ac, pst) →
                 SharedStateApprox sst sst1 i l rho envs)
         (IHHTrans2 : ∀ l : Label,
             ¬ labelleq pc l →
             ∀ (i : Tid) (pst1 : PrivateState) (sst : SharedState)
                    (pst : PrivateState) (ac : AnnoCmd) (sst1 : SharedState)
                    (ac1 : AnnoCmd),
               l = gsp (rho i) →
               pstateII pst t rho →
               SeqStep t rho (ac, (pst, sst)) (ac1, (pst1, sst1)) →
               ∀ pst0 : PrivateState,
                 starparaSeqStep t rho (ac2, pst0) (ac, pst) →
                 SharedStateApprox sst sst1 i l rho envs)
         (Hnlabelleq : ¬ labelleq pc l)

        destruct Hin as [x [ts'' [n'' [Hinx [Hpsx Hin]]]]].
        assert (labelleq (Lang.gsp (rho t)) (Lang.gsp (rho i))). {
          unfold pstoreII in HpsII.
          eapply HpsII; eauto.
        }
        match goal with [H: (_,_) = rho t |- _] ⇒ rewrite <- H in × end.
        simpl in ×.
        destruct Hnlabelleq.
        eauto with baselabel.
      × eapply in_tpc_union_in_tpc in Hin.
        destruct Hin as [ts'' [Hints Hin]].
        assert (labelleq (Lang.gsp (rho t)) (Lang.gsp (rho i))). {
          unfold tpcII in HtpcII.
          eapply HtpcII; eauto.
        }
        match goal with [H: (_,_) = rho t |- _] ⇒ rewrite <- H in × end.
        simpl in ×.
        destruct Hnlabelleq.
        eauto with baselabel.
  - simpl in ×.
    destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst0 [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep' HkparaSeqStep]]]]].
    inversion HSeqStep'.
    + subst.
      assert (ac = ASkip). {
        eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_is_Skip; eauto.
      }
      subst ac.
      inversion HSeqStep.
      eauto with basestate.
Qed.

Lemma starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq:
  ∀ c0 t rho ac pst sst ac1 pst1 sst1 envs pc i l envp' envp pst0 ac0
         (HTrans : Trans (c0, pc, rho t, envs, envp) (ac0, envp'))
         (HstarparaSeqStep: starparaSeqStep t rho (ac0, pst0) (ac, pst))
         (HSeqStep: SeqStep t rho (ac, (pst, sst)) (ac1, (pst1, sst1)))
         (Hnlabelleq: ¬ labelleq pc l)
         (Hl: l = gsp (rho i))
         (HpstII: pstateII pst t rho),
    SharedStateApprox sst sst1 i l rho envs.
Proof.
  intros.
  generalize dependent pst0.
  generalize dependent HSeqStep.
  generalize dependent HpstII.
  generalize dependent Hl.
  generalize dependent ac1.
  generalize dependent sst1.
  generalize dependent ac.
  generalize dependent pst.
  generalize dependent sst.
  generalize dependent pst1.
  generalize dependent i.
  generalize dependent l.
  remember (rho t) as v.
  generalize dependent Heqv.

  remember (
      fun (p:Cmd×Label×Policy×Env×Env) (p0: AnnoCmd×Env) ⇒
        match (p, p0) with
        | ((c0, pc, po, envs, envp), (ac0, envp')) ⇒
          po = rho t →
          ∀ l : Label,
            ¬ labelleq pc l →
            ∀ (i : Tid) (pst1 : PrivateState) (sst : SharedState) (pst : PrivateState)
                   (ac : AnnoCmd) (sst1 : SharedState) (ac1 : AnnoCmd),
              l = gsp (rho i) →
              pstateII pst t rho →

              SeqStep t rho (ac, (pst, sst)) (ac1, (pst1, sst1)) →
              ∀ pst0 : PrivateState,
                starparaSeqStep t rho (ac0, pst0) (ac, pst) → SharedStateApprox sst sst1 i l rho envs
        end
    ) as P.

  assert (P (c0,pc,v,envs, envp) (ac0, envp') =
          ((v = rho t) →
           ∀ l : Label,
             ¬ labelleq pc l →
             ∀ (i : Tid) (pst1 : PrivateState) (sst : SharedState) (pst : PrivateState)
                    (ac : AnnoCmd) (sst1 : SharedState) (ac1 : AnnoCmd),
               l = gsp (rho i) →
               pstateII pst t rho →
               SeqStep t rho (ac, (pst, sst)) (ac1, (pst1, sst1)) →
               ∀ pst0 : PrivateState,
                 starparaSeqStep t rho (ac0, pst0) (ac, pst) → SharedStateApprox sst sst1 i l rho envs
         ))
    as HP. {
    subst; auto.
  }
  rewrite <- HP; clear HP.


  induction HTrans; subst; intros; subst;
    try match goal with [H: starparaSeqStep _ _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into HstarparaSeqStep end;

    try match reverse goal with [H: SeqStep _ _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ rename H into HSeqStep end;
    try solve [
          intros;
          subst;
          destruct HstarparaSeqStep as [k HkparaSeqStep];
          destruct k;
          [
            simpl in *;
            inversion HkparaSeqStep;
            subst;
            inversion HSeqStep;
            subst;
            eauto with basestate
          |
          simpl in *;
          destruct HkparaSeqStep as [sst0 [ac'' [pst'' [sst'' [HSeqStep' HkparaSeqStep]]]]];
          inversion HSeqStep';
          subst;
          assert (ac = ASkip)
            by (eapply kparaSeqStep_Skip_is_Skip; eauto);
          subst ac;
          inversion HSeqStep;
          eauto with basestate]].

  - eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_Put; eauto.

  - eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_Out; eauto.

  - eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_Seq with (c1:=c1); eauto.

  - eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_If with (c1:=c1) (c2:=c2); eauto.

  - eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_While; eauto.
  - eapply IHHTrans2; eauto.

  - eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_Hsend; eauto.

  - eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_Lsend; eauto.

  - eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_Hrecv with (envp:=envp0) (envp':=envp'0); eauto.

  - eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq_Lrecv with (envp:=envp0) (envp':=envp'0); eauto.
Qed.

Lemma TSim_nlabelleq_pc_l:
  ∀ c01 ac01 c02 ac02 ac ac' pst pst' t l pc envp rho envs i envp' pst01 pst02 envp1 envp2
         (HTrans1 : Trans (c01, pc, rho t, envs, envp) (ac01, envp1))
         (HTrans2 : Trans (c02, pc, rho t, envs, envp) (ac02, envp2))
         (Hnlabelleq: ¬ labelleq pc l)
         (HstarparaSeqStep1: starparaSeqStep t rho (ac01, pst01) (ac, pst))
         (HstarparaSeqStep2: starparaSeqStep t rho (ac02, pst02) (ac', pst'))
         (HTTerm: ∀ sst02, ThreadTerm t rho ac02 pst02 sst02)
         (Henvleq1: leq_env envp1 envp')
         (Henvleq2: leq_env envp2 envp')
         (HPStateApprox: PStateApprox pst01 pst02 l pc envp)
         (Hl: l = gsp (rho i)),
    TSim ac ac' pst pst' t l pc envp' rho envs i.
Proof.
  cofix Hc.
  intros.
  apply TSimProceed.
  split.
  - intros.
    ∃ ac', pst', sst'.
    split.
    + ∃ O.
      simpl; auto.
    + split.
      × assert (SharedStateApprox sst sst1 i l rho envs). {
          match reverse goal with [H: seqstateII _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ destruct H end.
          eapply starparaSeqStep_SeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq with (c0:=c01) ; eauto.

        }
        eauto with basestate.
      × split.
        {
          eapply Hc with (ac01:=ac01); eauto.
          eapply SeqStep_starparaSeqStep; eauto.
        }
        split.
        -- eapply SeqStep_seqstateII; eauto.
        -- eapply SeqStep_seqstateII; eauto.
           econstructor; eauto.
  - intros.
    assert (∀ sst'' : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac' pst' sst''). {
      eapply starparaSeqStep_TTerm; eauto.
    }
    assert (∃ pst1' sst1', starSeqStep t rho (ac', (pst', sst')) (ASkip, (pst1', sst1'))) as HstarSeqStep. {
      eapply TTerm_starSeqStep_Skip; eauto.
    }
    destruct HstarSeqStep as [pst1' [sst1' HstarSeqStep]].
    ∃ pst1', sst1'.
    split; auto.
    split.
    + assert (SharedStateApprox sst' sst1' i l rho envs). {
        match goal with [H: seqstateII _ _ _ |- _] ⇒ destruct H end.
        eapply starparaSeqStep_starSeqStep_SStateApprox_nlabelleq; eauto.
      }
      eauto with basestate.
    + subst.
      assert (starparaSeqStep t rho (ac02, pst02) (ASkip, pst1')). {
        eapply starparaSeqStep_trans; eauto.
        eapply starSeqStep_starparaSeqStep; eauto.
        ∃ O; simpl; auto.
      }
      destruct pst as [tpc ps].
      destruct pst1' as [tpc1' ps1'].
      split.
      split.
      × intro.
        destruct Hnlabelleq; auto.
      × destruct pst01 as [tpc01 ps01].

        destruct pst02 as [tpc02 ps02].
        destruct HPStateApprox as [HPCApprox HPStoreApprox].
        unfold PStoreApprox.
        intros.
        remember (gsp (rho i)) as l.
        destruct (labelleq_dec pc (envp' x)) as [Hlabelleqpc | Hnlabelleqpc].
        -- subst lx.
           assert (labelleq pc l). {
             eauto with baselabel.
           }
           destruct Hnlabelleq; auto.
        -- assert (ps x = ps01 x). {
             eapply starparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq with (ac:=ac01) (envp':=envp1); eauto.
             eauto with baselabel baseenv.
           }
           assert (ps1' x = ps02 x). {
             eapply starparaSeqStep_Skip_psx_eq with (ac:=ac02) (envp' := envp2); eauto.
             eauto with baselabel baseenv.
           }
           unfold PStoreApprox in HPStoreApprox.
           remember (ps01 x) as v01.
           remember (ps02 x) as v02.
           apply eq_sym in Heqv01.
           apply eq_sym in Heqv02.
           destruct v01 as [ts01 n01].
           destruct v02 as [ts02 n02].
           assert (labelleq (envp x) l) as Hlabelleq. {
             subst.
             assert (envp1 x = envp x) as Henvp1x. {
               eapply Trans_nlabelleq_pc_label_eq; eauto.
               eauto with baselabel baseenv.
             }
             rewrite <- Henvp1x.
             eauto with baselabel.
           }
           specialize (HPStoreApprox x ts01 n01 ts02 n02 (envp x) eq_refl Heqv01 Heqv02 Hlabelleq).
           destruct HPStoreApprox.
           split; congruence.
      × eapply starSeqStep_seqstateII; eauto.
Qed.

Lemma WellType_imply_TSim_If_nlabelleq_lb_l:
  ∀ rho envs pc envp t l b c1 c2 ac1 ac2 lb envp1 envp2 i pst pst'
         (HTTerm': ∀ sst'0, ThreadTerm t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) pst' sst'0)
         (Hnlabelleq: ¬ labelleq lb l)
         (HTypeSafe: BexpTypeSafe envp b lb)
         (HTrans1 : Trans (c1, lunion pc lb, rho t, envs, envp) (ac1, envp1))
         (HTrans2 : Trans (c2, lunion pc lb, rho t, envs, envp) (ac2, envp2))
         (HTSim1 : ∀ pst pst' : PrivateState,
             PStateApprox pst pst' l (lunion pc lb) envp →
             (∀ sst0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac1 pst sst0) →

             TSim ac1 ac1 pst pst' t l (lunion pc lb) envp1 rho envs i)

             PStateApprox pst pst' l (lunion pc lb) envp →
             (∀ sst0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac2 pst sst0) →
             (∀ sst'0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac2 pst' sst'0) →
             
             
             TSim ac2 ac2 pst pst' t l (lunion pc lb) envp2 rho envs i)

         (HPStateApprox: PStateApprox pst pst' l pc envp),
         
         
    TSim (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) pst pst' t l pc
         (env_union envp1 envp2) rho envs i.

                            (ASeq ac1' AEnd, (ts' :: tpc', ps', sst'))). {

          simpl.
          eapply ex_intro.
          split; eauto.
          eapply SSSeq; eauto.
        }
        split; auto.
        split; auto.
        {

            by auto with baseenv.
          assert (TSim ac1' ac1' (ts :: tpc, ps) (ts' :: tpc', ps') t l (lunion pc lb) envp1 rho envs i).
          {
            eapply TSim_nlabelleq_pc_l with (ac01:=ac1') (ac02:=ac1'); eauto.
            - eauto with baselabel.
            - ∃ O.

              eapply Seq_TTerm_TTerm; eauto.

            - eauto with baseenv.
            - eapply PStateApprox_nlabelleq_pc_l; eauto with baselabel.

          assert (∀ sst0, ThreadTerm t rho (ASeq ac1' AEnd) (ts'::tpc', ps') sst0). {

                            (ASeq ac2 AEnd, (ts' :: tpc', ps', sst'))). {

        }
    
    + subst sst1.
      subst.
      remember (gsp (rho i)) as l.
      match goal with [H: BexpInterp _ _ = _ |- _ ] ⇒ rename H into Hbexpinterp end.
      generalize HPStateApprox; intro HPStateApprox_aux.
      destruct pst' as [tpc' ps'].
      destruct HPStateApprox as [HPStateApprox1 HPStateApprox2].
      rename HPStateApprox_aux into HPStateApprox.
      remember (BexpInterp b ps') as v eqn:Hbexpinterp' .
      apply eq_sym in Hbexpinterp'.
      destruct v as [ts' n'].
      destruct n'.
      × ∃ (ASeq ac1 AEnd), (ts'::tpc', ps'), sst'.
        assert (SeqStep t rho (AIfelse b ac1 ac1', (tpc', ps', sst')) (ac1, (ts' :: tpc', ps', sst'))) as HSeqStep'. {
          eapply SSIfelsetrue; eauto.
        }

        assert (starSeqStep t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac1') AEnd, (tpc', ps', sst'))
                            (ASeq ac1 AEnd, (ts' :: tpc', ps', sst'))). {
          ∃ (S O).
          simpl.
          eapply ex_intro.
          split; eauto.
          eapply SSSeq; eauto.
        }
        split; auto.
        split; auto.
        {
          assert (leq_env envp1 (env_union envp1 envp2))
            by auto with baseenv.
          assert (TSim ac1' ac1 (ts :: tpc, ps) (ts' :: tpc', ps') t l (lunion pc lb) (env_union envp1 envp2) rho envs i).
          {
            eapply TSim_nlabelleq_pc_l with (c02:=c1) (ac02:=ac1); eauto with baselabel.
            - ∃ O.
              simpl; eauto.
            - ∃ O.
              simpl; eauto.
            - eapply SeqStep_TTerm; eauto.
              intros.
              eapply Seq_TTerm_TTerm; eauto.
            - eauto with baseenv.
            - eapply PStateApprox_nlabelleq_pc_l; eauto with baselabel.
          }
          assert (∀ sst0, ThreadTerm t rho (ASeq ac1 AEnd) (ts'::tpc', ps') sst0). {
            eapply starSeqStep_TTerm; eauto.
          }
          assert (∀ sst0, ThreadTerm t rho ac1 (ts'::tpc', ps') sst0). {
            intros.
            eapply Seq_TTerm_TTerm; eauto.
          }
          assert (TSim (ASeq ac1' AEnd) (ASeq ac1 AEnd) (ts :: tpc, ps) (ts' :: tpc', ps') t l pc (env_union envp1 envp2) rho envs i).
          {
            eapply TSim_Seq_End with (ac0':=ac1); eauto with baseenv.
            eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
            eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
          }
          split.
          -- auto.

          -- split; eapply seqstateII_ifelse; eauto.

        }
      
      × ∃ (ASeq ac1' AEnd), (ts'::tpc', ps'), sst'.
        assert (SeqStep t rho (AIfelse b ac1 ac1', (tpc', ps', sst')) (ac1', (ts' :: tpc', ps', sst'))) as HSeqStep'. {
          eapply SSIfelsefalse; eauto.
        }
        assert (starSeqStep t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac1') AEnd, (tpc', ps', sst'))
                            (ASeq ac1' AEnd, (ts' :: tpc', ps', sst'))). {
          ∃ (S O).
          simpl.
          eapply ex_intro.
          split; eauto.
          eapply SSSeq; eauto.
        }
        split; auto.
        split; auto.
        {
          assert (leq_env envp1 (env_union envp1 envp2))
            by auto with baseenv.
          assert (TSim ac1' ac1' (ts :: tpc, ps) (ts' :: tpc', ps') t l (lunion pc lb) envp2 rho envs i).
          {
            eapply TSim_nlabelleq_pc_l; eauto.
            - eauto with baselabel.
            - ∃ O.
              simpl; eauto.
            - ∃ O.
              simpl; eauto.
            - eapply SeqStep_TTerm; eauto.
              intros.
              eapply Seq_TTerm_TTerm; eauto.
            - eauto with baseenv.
            - eauto with baseenv.
            - eapply PStateApprox_nlabelleq_pc_l; eauto with baselabel.
          }
          assert (∀ sst0, ThreadTerm t rho (ASeq ac1' AEnd) (ts'::tpc', ps') sst0). {
            eapply starSeqStep_TTerm; eauto.
          }
          assert (∀ sst0, ThreadTerm t rho ac1' (ts'::tpc', ps') sst0). {
            intros.
            eapply Seq_TTerm_TTerm; eauto.
          }
          assert (TSim (ASeq ac1' AEnd) (ASeq ac1' AEnd) (ts :: tpc, ps) (ts' :: tpc', ps') t l pc envp2 rho envs i).
          {
            eapply TSim_Seq_End; eauto with baseenv.
            eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
            eapply starparaSeqStep_refl; eauto.
          }
          
          split.
          -- eapply TSim_gt_envp with (envp:=envp2); eauto with baseenv.
          -- split; eapply seqstateII_ifelse; eauto.
        }
  
  - intros.
    congruence.
Qed.

Final Lemma

Lemma WellType_imply_TSim_If:
  ∀ rho envs pc envp t l b c1 c2 ac1 ac2 lb envp1 envp2 i pst pst'
         (HTTerm: ∀ sst'0, ThreadTerm t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) pst sst'0)
         (HTTerm': ∀ sst'0, ThreadTerm t rho (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) pst' sst'0)
         (HTypeSafe: BexpTypeSafe envp b lb)
         (HTrans1 : Trans (c1, lunion pc lb, rho t, envs, envp) (ac1, envp1))
         (HTrans2 : Trans (c2, lunion pc lb, rho t, envs, envp) (ac2, envp2))
         (HTSim1 : ∀ pst pst' : PrivateState,
             PStateApprox pst pst' l (lunion pc lb) envp →
             (∀ sst0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac1 pst sst0) →
             (∀ sst'0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac1 pst' sst'0) →
             
             
             TSim ac1 ac1 pst pst' t l (lunion pc lb) envp1 rho envs i)
         (HTSim2 : ∀ pst pst' : PrivateState,
             PStateApprox pst pst' l (lunion pc lb) envp →
             (∀ sst0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac2 pst sst0) →
             (∀ sst'0 : SharedState, ThreadTerm t rho ac2 pst' sst'0) →
             
             
             TSim ac2 ac2 pst pst' t l (lunion pc lb) envp2 rho envs i)
         (Hl: l = gsp (rho i))
         (HPStateApprox: PStateApprox pst pst' l pc envp),
         
         
    TSim (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) (ASeq (AIfelse b ac1 ac2) AEnd) pst pst' t l pc
         (env_union envp1 envp2) rho envs i.
Proof.
  intros.
  destruct (labelleq_dec lb l) as [Hlabelleq | Hnotlabelleq].
  - eapply WellType_imply_TSim_If_labelleq_lb_l; eauto.
  - eapply WellType_imply_TSim_If_nlabelleq_lb_l; eauto.
Qed.
